You hurl angry words against the people of the foreign lands that are hostile to @wDN{Nanna}. You are adorned with splendid horns, like a virile wild bull born to be a great wild bull. You are a chariot, a waggon set on the road. Like a noble ass, by your vigorous running you bring joy to @wDN{Enlil}.

